The Yacht & Country Club Membership Options
End Mini-Page 20084
Begin Mini-Page 20085
Equity
Members, along with their eligible family members, may enjoy a full-club amenity membership including unlimited access to the golf course, driving ranges, and practice facilities without tee time restrictions.  Amenities include the clubhouse, gourmet dining, fitness center, swimming pool, tennis, bocce, croquet, and pickle ball courts. As an Equity member, enjoy discounted guest rates, a choice of a Trail Fee, Prepaid Cart Fees, or Individual Cart Fees, and much more!
Executive
Qualifying members (currently employed), along with their eligible family members, may enjoy access to the golf course reserving afternoon tee times. Designed for the executive who works in the morning and plays golf in the afternoon.  Amenities include full access to driving ranges and practice facilities, clubhouse, gourmet dining, fitness center, swimming pool, tennis, bocce, croquet, and pickle ball courts. Cart fees apply.
Young Professional
Members ages 39 and under along with their eligible family members, may enjoy access to the golf course, driving ranges and practice facilities. Amenities include the clubhouse, gourmet dining, fitness center, swimming pool, tennis, bocce, croquet, and pickle ball courts. Cart fees apply.
Social
Members, along with their eligible family members, may enjoy access to the clubhouse, gourmet dining, fitness center, swimming pool, tennis, bocce, croquet, and pickle ball courts. Social members may also play golf once a month at guest rates and bring up to three (3) guests.
Introductory
Members, along with their eligible family members, may enjoy a four to six month “snapshot” of an annual full-club amenity membership between November 1st thru April 30th.  Amenities include unlimited access to the golf course, driving ranges, and practice facilities with no tee time restrictions.  Also included in the membership are the clubhouse, gourmet dining, fitness center, swimming pool, tennis, bocce, croquet, and pickle ball courts. Cart fees apply.
End Mini-Page 20085
